room_title: Escape room "The Study" by Med City Escape in Rochester (MN)
review: Great time! We did the Study room and it was a blast. I've done escape rooms at three other places and this was the most fun. Friendly staff as well. We will be going back soon.

room_title: Escape room "The Study" by Med City Escape in Rochester (MN)
review: We did 'The Study' with my boyfriend's family. Although we didn't manage to escape in time, everyone had a great time, and it was a unique way to spend time with each other. We will be going back to try the other challenges.

room_title: Escape room "The Study" by Med City Escape in Rochester (MN)
review: Had a wonderful time in The Study living an adventure as spies finding clues to the mad doctors evil plans and getting out without being caught! You really want to try this one!
